title: Republican Matt Van Epps defeats ‘AOC of Tennessee’ in close congressional special election
description: Aftyn Behn had raised Democrats’ hopes for an upset in the conservative stronghold after late polling showed the state lawmaker within striking distance of Van Epps, a former Army helicopter pilot backed by President Trump.
content:
Republican Matt Van Epps narrowly defeated Democrat Aftyn Behn in Tuesdays hotly contested special election for Tennessees 7th District House seat.
